name: Stranger Things
description: A group of young friends in a small town uncover a mystery involving secret experiments and supernatural forces.

name: Money Heist
description: A criminal mastermind plans the biggest heist in history, targeting the Royal Mint of Spain.

name: Breaking Bad
description: A high school chemistry teacher turned methamphetamine manufacturer partners with a former student to create a drug empire.

name: The Witcher
description: A monster hunter struggles to find his place in a world where people often prove more wicked than beasts.

name: Narcos
description: The rise and fall of the notorious Colombian drug kingpin Pablo Escobar and the DEA agents hunting him.

name: Squid Game
description: Hundreds of cash-strapped players accept a mysterious invitation to compete in deadly children's games for a huge prize.

name: Dark
description: A German sci-fi thriller about time travel, conspiracies, and the dark secrets of a small town.

name: Black Mirror
description: An anthology series exploring a twisted, high-tech world where humanity's greatest innovations and darkest instincts collide.

name: The Queen's Gambit
description: A young chess prodigy rises to fame while battling addiction and personal demons in the 1960s.

name: Peaky Blinders
description: A gangster family epic set in 1919 Birmingham, England, following the rise of the Peaky Blinders gang.
